Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "...It's not a bad haul. I found this.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Lucia opens the can with her trusty pocket knife and passes the can to Luna.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I ate already on my way back.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna nods, trusting the words of her older sister. Then she sips some of the broth packed with the synthesized meat inside the can.'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Lucia, when can I go out with you?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "But, you're always the one protecting me... It's my turn to protect you... Or at least, help...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "You're being good help for looking after our food stash.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "I promised our parents that I would never let anyone hurt you. So, I'll handle the riskier tasks...", 4: '1'}
